com.orgsync.api

Interface MembershipLogsResource


  • public interface MembershipLogsResource

    Access to the membership log entries resource from the OrgSync API. This allows a client to query the membership log entries based on the critera available in MembershipLogEntryRequest.

    See: https://api.orgsync.com/api/docs/v2/ org_membership_log_entries

    • Method Summary

      Methods

      ListenableFuture<ApiResponse<List<MembershipLogEntry>>> getLogEntries(MembershipLogEntryRequest request)
      Get the membership log entries that match the criteria specified in the request.
